# New TunePad cell for piano 
# Keys cell (no imports) — Em → Bm → D → A progression
# Em = [52,55,59] ; Bm = [47,50,54] ; D = [50,54,57] ; A = [57,61,64]

progression = [
    [52, 55, 59],   # Em  (E3 G3 B3)
    [47, 50, 54],   # Bm  (B2 D3 F#3)
    [50, 54, 57],   # D   (D3 F#3 A3)
    [57, 61, 64]    # A   (A3 C#4 E4)
]
for i in range(0, 24):   
    for chord in progression:
        playNote(chord, beats=4, velocity=70)
